item.title: Jadakiss Scores No. 1 Return on Top R&B/Hip-Hop Albums | Billboard
item.description:
Jadakiss Scores No. 1 Return on Top R&B/Hip-Hop Albums | Billboard

Rapper Jadakiss returns to No. 1 on Top R&B/Hip-Hop Albums (chart dated Dec. 12) as Top 5 Dead Or Alive arrives with 60,000 sold in the week ending Nov. 26, according to Nielsen Music. The entrance marks his third chart leader (as a solo act) and first crowning set since 2009 when his third studio album The Last Kiss bowed atop the tally.

item.title: Drake Releases Visual Ode To L.A. Ahead Of OVO Store Opening
item.description:
Drake Releases Visual Ode To L.A. Ahead Of OVO Store Opening

Although fans are still awaiting the arrival of Drake's Views From The 6, the Toronto native blessed his support base with a new video. Now, the visual doesn't entail anything specifically about his forthcoming project, but it does have something to do with his OVO imprint.
